\( c_0 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR

\( c_1 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR

\( c_2 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR

\( c_3 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR

\( c_4 = \) \{ans_rule(20)\}  $BR$BR

Find the radius of convergence \( R \) of the series. $BR 
\( R = \)  \{ans_rule(20)\}  .
END_TEXT

ANS(num_cmp($a) );
ANS(num_cmp(0) );
ANS(num_cmp("-$a*$b") );
ANS(num_cmp(0) );
ANS(num_cmp("$a*$b^2") );
ANS(num_cmp("1/$b1") );

